title: NFL Around the League: August 7th, 2013
itunes:title: NFL Around the League: August 7th, 2013
description:
Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Kevin Patra discuss the highs and lows of HBO’s premiere episode of Hard Knocks, chronicling the best moments of the Cincinnati Bengals’ 2013 season. The crew wants your help in choosing the podcast’s new intro music. Vote via Twitter between #BarryWhite #Batman and the #Renaissance music selections using the hash-tag #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
